    6440 [label=<Google Policy Classification: <B><FONT COLOR="/svg/black">reciprocal</FONT></B><BR />reciprocal - These licenses allow usage of software made available under such<BR />licenses freely in *unmodified* form. If the third-party source code is modified<BR />in any way these modifications to the original third-party source code must be<BR />made available.>
